Trekkies;;70;;85;;PG;;The science fiction TV franchise "Star Trek" has had a seismic impact on the lives of its most obsessive fans. Known as Trekkies, these diehard devotees wear their Starfleet costumes in public, speak in Klingon and even redecorate their offices and homes to mimic the look of the "Star Trek" world. In this documentary, former "Star Trek" actress Denise Crosby travels the country interviewing famous fans like Barbara Adams and exploring the reasons behind the show's enduring appeal.;;Documentary;;Roger Nygard;;1999;;Denise Crosby,Barbara Adams,Denis Bourguignon,David Greenstein,Laurel Greenstein,Gabriel KÃ¶erner,Richard Koerner,Rich Kronfeld,Joyce Mason,Evelyn De Biase,Anne Kathleen Murphy,Majel Roddenberry,James Doohan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/trekkies